     F*****************************************************************
     F*                                                               *
     F*  Midas - User Defined Correspondence                          *
     F*                                                               *
     F*  CG6011 - Transfer of Principal Confirmations - Driver        *
     F*                                                               *
     F*  Function:  Lending Principal Increase Confirmations driver   *
     F*  (COB)      will read through file CONFS and process only the *
     F*             records with an amendment type of 'PI' and a      *
     F*             confirmation indicator of 'Y'.  The UDC data      *
     F*             extracted will be for group set l11PT.  An audit  *
     F*             report will be produced.                          *
     F*                                                               *
     F*  Called By: CGC6002 - COB Confirmation Processing.            *
     F*                                                               *
     F*  Calls:     CG6016  - Transfer of Principal Confirmations -   *
     F*                       Extract                                 *
