     FCONFS   UF  E           K        DISK
     F                                              KINFSR SRFILE
     F                                              KCOMIT
     F            LOAMSDHF                          KIGNORE
     F            LOAMSZ1F                          KIGNORE
     FLENXTAA UF  E                    DISK                      A
     F                                              KINFSR SRFILE
     F                                              KCOMIT
     FLENXTAB O   E                    DISK                      A
     F                                              KINFSR SRFILE
     F                                              KCOMIT
     FLENXTAC UF  E                    DISK                      A
     F                                              KINFSR SRFILE
     F                                              KCOMIT
      /TITLE FUNCTION OF INDICATORS
     F*****************************************************************
     F*                                                               *
     F*  F U N  C T I O N    O F    I N D I C A T O R S               *
     F*                                                               *
     F*  50   -    EOF indicator for CONFS                            *
     F*  60   -    EOF indicator for LENXTAA, LENXTAC                 *
     F*  90   -    General work indicator                             *
     F*                                                               *
     F*****************************************************************
      /TITLE SUBROUTINE INDEX
     F*****************************************************************
     F*                                                               *
     F*  S U B R O U T I N E    I N D E X                             *
     F*                                                               *
     F*  Main routine                                                 *
     F*  SRINIT  -  Initial Processing                                *
     F*  SRINZF  -  Initialise Fields on Program Invocation           *
     F*  SRMAIN  -  Main Processing                                   *
     F*  SRWLEN  -  Write to LENXTAA, LENXTAB, LENXTAC                *
     F*  SRAUDT  -  Audit Report Processing                           *
     F*  *PSSR   -  Error Subroutine                                  *
     F*                                                               *
     F*****************************************************************
     E/EJECT
     E*****************************************************************
     E*
     E**  Copyright array.
     E                    CPY@    1   1 80
     E/COPY CGCPYSRC,SRERRE
     I/EJECT
     I*
     IDSPARM    E DSCONFSDK
     I**  External DS for parameter passed to CG6016
     I*
     IW0FMT     E DSCGUDTAPD
     I**  Record format of PF/CGUDTAPD for use as a parameter
     I/COPY CGCPYSRC,CGAUDTI
     I/COPY CGCPYSRC,SRERRI
     C/EJECT
     C*****************************************************************
     C*                                                               *
     C*  Process     :  MAINLINE                                      *
     C*  Function    :  Mainline processing.                          *
     C*                                                               *
     C*  Called by   :  None                                          *
     C*  Calls       :  SRINIT - Initial Processing - On First Call   *
     C*                 SRINZF - Initialise Fields on Each Invocation *
     C*                 SRMAIN - Main Processing                      *
     C*                 SRAUDT - Audit Report Processing              *
     C*                                                               *
     C*****************************************************************
     C*
     C**  Parameter list for current program invocation.
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           W0RTN
     C                     PARM           W0CMT   3
     C*
     C**  Set up subroutine stack name
     C                     ADD  1         Q
     C                     MOVEL'MAIN'    @STK,Q
     C*
     C**  Initial processing - Once Only
     C*
     C           ##INIT    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     EXSR SRINIT
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ##INIT  1
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C**  Initialisation processing
     C                     EXSR SRINZF
     C*
     C**  Main processing
     C                     EXSR SRMAIN
     C*
     C**  Audit Processing
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT
     C*
     C**  Unwind subroutine stack name
     C                     MOVEA*BLANKS   @STK,Q
     C                     SUB  1         Q
     C*
     C**  Terminate program
     C                     RETRN
     C*
     C*****************************************************************
     C/EJECT
     C*****************************************************************
     C*                                                               *
     C*  Process     :  SRMAIN                                         *
     C*  Function    :  Main Processing                               *
     C*                                                               *
     C*  Called by   :  Mainline                                      *
     C*  Calls          CG6016 - Transfer of Principal Confirmations  *
     C*                          Extract                              *
     C*                 SRWLEN - Write to LENXTAA, LENXTAB, LENXTAC   *
     C*                                                               *
     C*****************************************************************
     C           SRMAIN    BEGSR
     C*
     C**  Set up subroutine stack name
     C                     ADD  1         Q       50
     C                     MOVEL'SRMAIN'  @STK,Q
     C*
     C** Read through CONFS file.
     C*
     C           *LOVAL    SETLLLOAMSDKF
     C                     READ CONFS                    50
     C*
     C** Read until End of File
     C*
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ'0'
     C*
     C** If Confirmation indicator = 'Y' and amendment type = 'PT'
     C*
     C           AMTP      IFEQ 'PT'
     C           CNFY      ANDEQ'Y'
     C*
     C**  Increment the count of CONFS records read.
     C                     ADD  1         ##DREC  50
     C*
     C** Produce Confirmation
     C*
     C                     CALL 'CG6016'
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   ##RTCD  7
     C                     PARM W0CMT     ##CMT   3
     C                     PARM *BLANK    ##COPD  1
     C                     PARM *BLANK    ##AUTO  1
     C                     PARM           DSPARM
     C*
     C**  Error in called program.
     C           ##RTCD    IFNE *BLANK
     C*
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT
     C*
     C** Database error
     C                     MOVEL'CG6016  'W0FILE           ***************
     C                     MOVEL##RTCD    W0KEY            * DB ERROR 01 *
     C                     Z-ADD01        W0ERNB           ***************
     C                     MOVEL'MEM5003' W0MSGD
     C                     MOVEL'MIDAS  ' W0MSGF
     C                     EXSR SRERR
     C                     END
     C*
     C** Confirmation Produced?
     C*
     C           ##COPD    IFEQ 'Y'
     C*
     C** Update Confirmation indicator on CONFS
     C*
     C                     MOVEL'N'       CNFY
     C                     UPDATLOAMSDKF
     C*
     C** Write to LENXTAA, LENXTAB, LENXTAC if auto-transmission of confirmation
     C*
     C           ##AUTO    IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     EXSR SRWLEN
     C                     END
     C*
     C                     END                             * ##COPD= 'Y'
     C*
     C                     END                             * CNFY='Y'/AMTP='PI'
     C*
     C** Commit
     C                     COMIT
     C*
     C** Read next record from CONFS
     C*
     C                     READ CONFS                    50
     C                     END                             * *IN50 DOWEQ '0'
     C*
     C           EXMAIN    TAG
     C*
     C**  Unwind subroutine stack name
     C                     MOVEA*BLANKS   @STK,Q
     C                     SUB  1         Q
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*****************************************************************
     C/EJECT
     C*****************************************************************
     C*                                                               *
     C*  Process    :  SRWLEN                                         *
     C*  Function   :  Write to LENXTAA, LENXTAB, LENXTAC             *
     C*                                                               *
     C*  Called by   :  SRMAIN - Main processing.                     *
     C*  Calls       :                                                *
     C*                                                               *
     C*****************************************************************
     C           SRWLEN    BEGSR
     C*
     C**  Set up subroutine stack name
     C                     ADD  1         Q       50
     C                     MOVEL'SRWLEN'  @STK,Q
     C*
     C** Write to detail file - LENXTAB
     C*
     C                     Z-ADDVDAT      VDATS
     C                     Z-ADDLASN      LASNS
     C                     MOVE LWOI      LWDI
     C                     Z-ADDFTYP      FTYPS
     C                     MOVE PONI      PONIA
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   CSID
     C                     Z-ADDTNLU      ORED
      *
     C                     WRITELENXTABF
     C*
     C** Write to header file - LENXTAA
     C*
     C           1         CHAINLENXTAA              60
     C           *IN60     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL'H'       RECI
     C                     WRITELENXTAAF
     C                     END
     C*
     C** Write to trailer file - LENXTAC
     C*
     C           1         CHAINLENXTAC              60
     C           *IN60     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVEL'T'       RECI
     C                     Z-ADD1         NORES
     C                     WRITELENXTACF
     C                     ELSE
     C                     ADD  1         NORES
     C                     UPDATLENXTACF
     C                     END
     C*
     C           EXWLEN    TAG
     C*
     C**  Unwind subroutine stack name
     C                     MOVEA*BLANKS   @STK,Q
     C                     SUB  1         Q
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*****************************************************************
     C/EJECT
     C*****************************************************************
     C*                                                               *
     C*  Process     :  SRINZF                                        *
     C*  Function    :  Initialise Fields on Program Invocation       *
     C*                                                               *
     C*  Called by   :  Mainline                                      *
     C*  Calls       :  CGZAUDIT - Audit Processing                   *
     C*                                                               *
     C*****************************************************************
     C           SRINZF    BEGSR
     C*
     C**  Set up subroutine stack name
     C                     ADD  1         Q
     C                     MOVEL'SRINZF'  @STK,Q
     C*
     C**  Open the Audit Print File.
     C                     CLEARI#DTA
     C                     MOVEL'CG6011AU'I#SPLN
     C                     MOVEL'CG6011  'I#REF
     C                     MOVE 'CGD2527' I#TITL
     C                     MOVE 'CGD2528' I#TUL
     C                     MOVEL'CGUSRMSG'I#FILE
     C*
     C                     CALL 'CGZAUDIT'
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   W0RTN   7
     C                     PARM '*OPEN   'W0ACT   8
     C                     PARM           I#DTA
     C                     PARM           W0RSQN  5
     C*
     C           EXINZF    TAG
     C*
     C**  Unwind subroutine stack name
     C                     MOVEA*BLANKS   @STK,Q
     C                     SUB  1         Q
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*****************************************************************
     C/EJECT
     C*****************************************************************
     C*                                                               *
     C*  Process     :  SRINIT                                        *
     C*  Function    :  Initial Processing - First Call Only          *
     C*                                                               *
     C*  Called by   :  Mainline                                      *
     C*  Calls       :  None                                          *
     C*                                                               *
     C*****************************************************************
     C           SRINIT    BEGSR
     C*
     C**  Set up subroutine stack name
     C                     ADD  1         Q
     C                     MOVEL'SRINIT'  @STK,Q
     C*
     C**  Initialise work fields
     C                     Z-ADD*ZEROS    ##DREC
     C*
     C**  Copyright
     C                     MOVEACPY@      ACT@   80
     C*
     C           EXINIT    TAG
     C*
     C**  Unwind subroutine stack name
     C                     MOVEA*BLANKS   @STK,Q
     C                     SUB  1         Q
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*****************************************************************
     C/EJECT
     C*****************************************************************
     C*                                                               *
     C*  Process    :  SRAUDT                                         *
     C*  Function   :  Audit Report Processing                        *
     C*                                                               *
     C*  Called by   :  Mainline                                      *
     C*  Calls       :  CGZAUDIT - Audit Processing                   *
     C*                 CG9020   - Write Data to UDC Data Files-Audit *
     C*                                                               *
     C*****************************************************************
     C           SRAUDT    BEGSR
     C*
     C**  Set up subroutine stack name
     C                     ADD  1         Q
     C                     MOVEL'SRAUDT'  @STK,Q
     C*
     C**  Output the Count of records read
     C                     CLEARI#DTA
     C                     MOVEL'CG6011  'I#REF
     C                     MOVE 'CGD2527' I#TITL
     C                     MOVE 'CGD2528' I#TUL
     C                     MOVEL'CGUSRMSG'I#FILE
     C                     MOVE '*LINE   'W1ACT
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   I#SUB
     C                     MOVEL'CONFS   'I#SUB
     C                     MOVEL'CAD1021' I#TEXT
     C                     Z-ADD##DREC    I#QTY
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     I#DECS
     C                     MOVE '1'       I#EDIT
     C*
     C                     CALL 'CGZAUDIT'
     C                     PARM           W1RTN   7
     C                     PARM           W1ACT   8
     C                     PARM           I#DTA
     C                     PARM           W1RSQN  5
     C*
     C**  Skip a line.
     C                     MOVE '*SKIP   'W1ACT
     C*
     C                     CALL 'CGZAUDIT'
     C                     PARM           W1RTN   7
     C                     PARM           W1ACT   8
     C                     PARM           I#DTA
     C                     PARM           W1RSQN  5
     C*
     C**  Produce the Audit Report.
     C                     CALL 'CG9020'
     C                     PARM *BLANK    ##RTCD
     C                     PARM '*AUDIT  'W0ACT
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   W0PATH256
     C                     PARM           W0FMT
     C                     PARM 'CGD2527' W0TITL  7
     C                     PARM 'CGD2528' W0ULIN  7
     C                     PARM           W0CMT
     C*
     C**  Close the Audit Print File.
     C                     CLEARI#DTA
     C                     MOVEL'CG6011  'I#REF
     C                     MOVE 'CGD2527' I#TITL
     C                     MOVE 'CGD2528' I#TUL
     C                     MOVEL'CGUSRMSG'I#FILE
     C*
     C                     CALL 'CGZAUDIT'
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   ##RTCD
     C                     PARM '*CLOSE  'W0ACT   8
     C                     PARM           I#DTA
     C                     PARM           W0RSQN  5
     C*
     C           EXAUDT    TAG
     C*
     C**  Unwind subroutine stack name
     C                     MOVEA*BLANKS   @STK,Q
     C                     SUB  1         Q
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*****************************************************************
     C/EJECT
     C/COPY CGCPYSRC,SRERRPSSR
     C/EJECT
     C/COPY CGCPYSRC,SRERRC
     C/EJECT
